2. cs.OH (Optical Networking and Communication): The paper specifically focuses on optical communication systems and proposes a new sampling scheme for them. 
3. cs.PH (Physics and Society): The paper involves the application of physics concepts to develop a new sampling scheme for optical communication systems. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses a technique to improve the performance of optical communication systems, which is a topic related to networking and internet architecture. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the sampling of wideband signals, which is a topic related to multimedia processing.
